    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.poster.avif?t=1704815356\" width=600 height=52 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.webm?t=1704815356\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/6271803a27097d20d9a274f210b3f826.mp4?t=1704815356\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Launch into a relentless roguelike action experience in this top-down shooter with bombs!<br><br>In a robotic world, control Lizzy and their band of unlockable beasty bots, each hungry for upgrades to enhance their abilities. However, the precious resources required are guarded by Steel Sentinels, guardians of the arena. Your mission is to outmaneuver these sentinels, collect valuable upgrades, and create powerful, game-changing synergies. Will you outsmart these mechanical wardens and survive the treacherous arena to build the ultimate beasty bot?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Many weapons</strong>: bombs, mines, missiles, and special bullet ammunition types like metal, poison, fire, and ice.<br></li><li> <strong>Resource gathering</strong>: Destroy enemies and breakable blocks to get resources necessary to upgrade your animal bot.<br></li><li> <strong>Customizable Upgrades</strong>: Combine over 60+ unique upgrades for powerful and diverse gameplay strategies.<br></li><li> <strong>Varied Encounters</strong>: Experience diverse gameplay with randomized enemy types, spawn points, and resource distribution within levels, creating unique encounters each playthrough.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LIZZY BOT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/94a7874cb56b6844d1fd79dffb936055.avif?t=1704815356\" width=500 height=497 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BAMBI BOT (unlockable)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/ec2bb207ffd219bdec5f909feba2aafb.avif?t=1704815356\" width=500 height=508 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FOXY BOT (unlockable)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/b9beb59a23b728cb8826b507f9561b79.avif?t=1704815356\" width=500 height=508 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RABBY BOT (unlockable)</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343820/extras/1b2f020b438f4f13902cc10b84e9a9f8.avif?t=1704815356\" width=500 height=561 /></span>",
